title: Episode 378: Think Big, Bitch (Feat. Mashonda Tifrere & Cassandra Cummings)
itunes:title: Episode 378: Think Big, Bitch (Feat. Mashonda Tifrere & Cassandra Cummings)
description:
Singer/songwriter, Mashonda Tifrere and financial expert, Cassandra Cummings join the ladies for Lip Service this week; Mashonda to promote her latest EP 'Note to Self,' and Cassandra to promote her book 'Fearless Finances.' The ladies discuss dating later in life when the woman is financially stable, dating younger men, and much more. Mashonda even admits to leaving a man while on vacation with him...enjoy!
